<p><a name="France" id="France"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Black_Madonna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: France">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">France</span></h4>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Guingamp-madonna.jpg" class="image" title="La Vierge noire de Guingamp"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Guingamp-madonna.jpg/250px-Guingamp-madonna.jpg" width="250" height="212" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Guingamp-madonna.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
La Vierge noire de <a href="/wiki/Guingamp" title="Guingamp">Guingamp</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Many examples exist, including:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Aix-en-Provence" title="Aix-en-Provence">Aix-en-Provence</a>: in <a href="/wiki/Aix_Cathedral" title="Aix Cathedral">Cathédrale Saint-Sauveur d'Aix</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Arbois" title="Arbois">Arbois</a>, <a href="/wiki/Jura_(department)" title="Jura (department)">Jura</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Arceau" title="Arceau">Arceau</a>, <a href="/wiki/C%C3%B4te-d%27Or" title="Côte-d'Or">Côte-d'Or</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Arconsat" title="Arconsat">Arconsat</a>, <a href="/wiki/Puy-de-D%C3%B4me" title="Puy-de-Dôme">Puy-de-Dôme</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Aurillac" title="Aurillac">Aurillac</a>, <a href="/wiki/Cantal" title="Cantal">Cantal</a> <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Aurillac.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Aurillac.html" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Avioth" title="Avioth">Avioth</a>, <a href="/wiki/Meuse" title="Meuse">Meuse</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Chartres" title="Chartres">Chartres</a>, <a href="/wiki/Eure-et-Loir" title="Eure-et-Loir">Eure-et-Loir</a>: crypt of the <a href="/wiki/Chartres_Cathedral" title="Chartres Cathedral">Cathedral of Chartres</a> <a href="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/notre-dame.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/notre-dame.html" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Clermont-Ferrand" title="Clermont-Ferrand">Clermont-Ferrand</a>, Puy de Dôme <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/ClermontFerrand.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/ClermontFerrand.html" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Guingamp" title="Guingamp">Guingamp</a>, Brittany, Basilica of Notre Dame de Bon Secour.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/La_Chapelle-Geneste" title="La Chapelle-Geneste">La Chapelle-Geneste</a>, <a href="/wiki/Haute-Loire" title="Haute-Loire">Haute-Loire</a> <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/LCGeneste.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/LCGeneste.html" rel="nofollow">[4]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Le_Puy-en-Velay" title="Le Puy-en-Velay">Le Puy-en-Velay</a>, Haute-Loire <a href="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/mainaltar.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/mainaltar.html" rel="nofollow">[5]</a> <a href="http://photo.net/photodb/photo?photo_id=6615900" class="external autonumber" title="http://photo.net/photodb/photo?photo_id=6615900" rel="nofollow">[6]</a> <a href="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/other_madonna.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/other_madonna.html" rel="nofollow">[7]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Marseille" title="Marseille">Marseille</a>: Saint Victor</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mauriac,_Cantal" title="Mauriac, Cantal">Mauriac</a>, Cantal <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Mauriac.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Mauriac.html" rel="nofollow">[8]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Meymac" title="Meymac">Meymac</a>, <a href="/wiki/Corr%C3%A8ze" title="Corrèze">Corrèze</a> <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Meymac.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Meymac.html" rel="nofollow">[9]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Myans" title="Myans">Myans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Savoie" title="Savoie">Savoie</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Rocamadour" title="Rocamadour">Rocamadour</a>: Our Lady of Rocamadour <a href="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/rocamadour.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.aracnet.com/~sbvoices/rocamadour.html" rel="nofollow">[10]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Saint-Jean-Cap-Ferrat" title="Saint-Jean-Cap-Ferrat">Saint-Jean-Cap-Ferrat</a>, <a href="/wiki/Alpes-Maritimes" title="Alpes-Maritimes">Alpes Maritimes</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Tarascon" title="Tarascon">Tarascon</a>, <a href="/wiki/Bouches-du-Rh%C3%B4ne" title="Bouches-du-Rhône">Bouches-du-Rhône</a>: Notre-Dame du Château <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Tarascon.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Tarascon.html" rel="nofollow">[11]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Thuret,_Puy-de-D%C3%B4me" title="Thuret, Puy-de-Dôme">Thuret</a>, Puy-du-Dome <a href="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Thuret.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://shell.amigo.net/~ma3/Thuret.html" rel="nofollow">[12]</a></li>
</ul>
