<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Black_Madonna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Black Madonnas or important replicas in the Americas">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Black Madonnas or important replicas in the Americas</span></h2>
<p><a name="Brazil" id="Brazil"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Black_Madonna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Brazil">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Brazil</span></h4>
